## 启动/重启监控服务

```bash
# 启动 Control Center UI
cd /root/openclaw-control-center
npm run dev:ui

# 后台运行（生产环境）
nohup npm run dev:ui > /root/.openclaw/logs/control-center.log 2>&1 &

# 重启服务
pkill -f "tsx src/index.ts"
npm run dev:ui &
```

---

## 验证监控正常

```bash
# 1. 检查服务端口
ss -tlnp | grep 4310

# 2. 测试 API
curl http://127.0.0.1:4310/api/docker/containers | python3 -m json.tool

# 3. 访问网页
curl -s "http://127.0.0.1:4310/?section=nanchaoyi-monitor&lang=zh" | grep -o "<h2>.*</h2>"
```

